high_descs: Cross the room to the stove in front of you and turn to face the counter to your left.
Pick up the knife on the counter next to the lettuce.
Turn around and walk around the kitchen island to stand in front of the bread
Slice the bread with the knife
Turn to your right and walk to the recycling bin in the corner
Place the knife into the recycling bin
Turn around and walk back to the sliced bread
Pick up the end slice from the bread on the counter
Turn to your left and walk all the way around the kitchen island until you reach the microwave
Open the microwave and place the bread inside the microwave and cook it before removing it
Turn to your left and walk back around the island to the recycling bin
Place the bread into the recycling bin
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked piece of bread into the recycling bin

high_descs: Move forward and face the counter to your left next to the fridge.
Pick up the knife on your right on the counter.
Turn left, then left again and face the counter with the bread on top on your left.
Slice the bread on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the blue recycling bin in front of you.
Place the knife in the recycling bin in front of you.
Turn right then face the counter on your right with the bread on it.
Take a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn left, then right around the counter and face the microwave to your left.
Heat up the bread in the microwave in front of you, take out the bread and close the microwave.
Turn left, then left again around the counter and face the recycling bin on your right.
Place the slice of bread in the recycling bin in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot piece of bread in the recycling bin.

high_descs: Go to the kitchen and face left.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around to go to the far side of the island with a loaf of bread.
Slice the bread on the table.
Turn around and go to the recycling bin.
Place the knife inside the recycling bin.
Turn around to go back to the island.
Pick up one slice of bread.
Go around the island to get to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the slice of bread and heat it.
Take the slice out of the microwave and head back to the recycling bin.
Place the slice in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of bread in the recycling bin.

high_descs: Walk forward and face the counter on the left to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn to the left and walk around the table and turn left to face the table.
Cut the full loaf of bread on the table.
Turn around walk forward to the trash bin.
Place the knife into the trash bin.
Turn around and walk forward to face the table with a loaf of bread on it.
Pick up a slice of bread from on the counter.
Turn and walk around the room to face the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the trash bin.
Put the slice of bread into the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of bread, as well as put the bread plus a knife into the trash bin.
